g.text: Starts the option to consult the users in the waiting room
returns list of the users in the waiting room
[while list of the users in the waiting room has users]
Returns the list of the users in the waiting room
[list with users in the waiting room isn't empty]
gets all the other wanted atributtes of the SNSUser (sex, birth date, SNS number, phone number)
Returns the list of the users in the waiting room
[list with users in the waiting room is empty]
Message: "There are no users on the waiting room."
